subject: Gymnastics
Suits and Litigation
lead_paragraph: The lawyer for a Chinese gymnast says she has settled claims against the United States Gymnastics Federation and insurance companies after she was paralyzed in a vaulting accident at the 1998 Goodwill Games in New York.
